title: Ayodhya gang rape: Allahabad HC bench junks Samajwadi Party man's bail plea
title_detail: {'type': 'text/plain', 'language': 'en-US', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeeds/3947060.cms', 'value': "Ayodhya gang rape: Allahabad HC bench junks Samajwadi Party man's bail plea"}

title: 1 dead, 2 injured in road accident in Kaushambi, Uttar Pradesh
title_detail: {'type': 'text/plain', 'language': 'en-US', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeeds/3947060.cms', 'value': '1 dead, 2 injured in road accident in Kaushambi, Uttar Pradesh'}
summary: A speeding DCM truck caused a road accident near Chandwari turn in Kaushambi district. The truck rammed into a roadside barber shop, killing a 55-year-old man on the spot. Two people were injured and admitted to the hospital. Locals blocked the Kanpur-Prayagraj highway in protest, but police managed to calm the situation.
